{{wikipediapar|Paget's disease of bone}}
==English==
===Etymology===
Named after British [[surgeon]] [[w:James Paget|James Paget]] (1814-1899) who was the first to describe this disease.
===Noun===
'''Paget's [[disease]]'''
# The bone disease [[osteitis deformans]].
